      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SHE'S CAPITANA (10) comes back to a CL1 today after tackling tougher races to begin this campaign where she's been right in the mix. Pike hops back on board and she does possess some early speed. Building nicely this time in work and this looks a very winnable race. ESPINHO (1) jumped favourite in a similar race first-up when only 2.4L off the winner. Fitter for that effort and Brad Parnham now takes the ride and he closed off very strongly in that fresh performance. Fitter now and can be right in the finish again. SCENIC GEORGE (2) will find this a little easier than his latest effort and he beat home ESPINHO on that occasion. Nottle hops on board and he should get every chance from the draw. TRUE FICTION (5) can play a leading role on resumption with Harvey in the saddle. STAR SUPREME (6) will be fitter for the fresh effort and he won't be far away.",
